<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2026</p>

<p>
AfterCallPro (“we,” “our,” or “us”) is operated by MindRocket Systems LLC.
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information
when you use our website and services.
</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Contact information you provide (such as name, email, or phone number)</li>
  <li>Call data, transcripts, and metadata generated through use of the service</li>
  <li>Basic usage data to improve performance and reliability</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Information</h2>
<p>
We use information solely to operate, maintain, and improve AfterCallPro,
including providing AI call answering, summaries, and related features.
</p>

<h2>Data Sharing</h2>
<p>
We do not sell your personal information. Data may be shared only with
service providers necessary to operate the platform (such as hosting,
telecom, or AI processing providers).
</p>

<h2>Data Security</h2>
<p>
We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data.
However, no system can be guaranteed to be 100% secure.
</p>

<h2>Your Choices</h2>
<p>
You may request access, correction, or deletion of your data by contacting us.
</p>

